    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A cheap, adjustable loop of faux-leather, cloth, or plastic, designed to be placed and tightened around the user's wrist. Installable in any weapon. Cannot be used while the weapon is holstered; enabling/disabling the strap's functionality requires an action after the weapon is equipped.</p><p>While wearing the strap, the weapon it's attached to cannot be dropped, thrown, or holstered. If removed from the user's hand, the weapon hangs from their wrist and can be reequipped without using an action. While a weapon is hanging from the user's arm in this way, any subsequent attacks made with that arm/hand suffer a cumulative -1 penalty for each hand the hanging weapon requires.</p>"
